spaska.gui

Interface Parametrable

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IAnalyzer, IClassifier, IClusterer, ICompareAnalyzer, Validator
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CrossValidation, DecisionTree, KNN, NormalizeValidator, OneR, PairedTTest, SimpleKMeans, TwoLayerPerceptron, Wilcoxon, ZeroClusterer, ZeroR

    public interface Parametrable
    The GUI must set the properties of different kind of objects. Each object that needs to set some parameters needs to implement this interface. Each Parameterable class needs to implement public static Map getParameters() that needs to return all the properties that needs to be set and their default values. If no parameters set is required return null;
    Author:
    Vesko Georgiev
